#include <iostream>

#define SD(a) scanf("%d", &a)
#define PD(a) printf("%d ", a)

int main () {
	int seq[10000], cnt = 0, status = 0;
	for (; SD(seq[cnt]) != EOF; ++cnt);
	for (int i = 0; i < cnt; i++) {
		for (int j = 0; j < cnt - 1; ++j) {
			if (seq[j] > seq[j+1]) {
				seq[j] = seq[j] ^ seq[j+1];
				seq[j+1] = seq[j] ^ seq[j+1];
				seq[j] = seq[j] ^ seq[j+1];
				status = 1;
			}
			PD(seq[j]);
		}
		PD(seq[cnt - 1]);
		if (status == 0)
			break;
		status = 0;
		puts("");
	}
	return 0;
}
